Limited edition Apple Watch is made with 24 karat gold, rose gold or platinum and your choice of strap - including python skin . 
  The watches are the latest expensive gift from luxury electronics firm Goldgenie . 
  One version of the watch is adorned with a one carat diamond plus hundreds of other smaller diamonds in the strap . 
  They are part of the Apple Watch Spectrum Collection and are available to order now . 
  The Apple Watch will go on sale in the UK on April 24 . 
 